minutes or hours.

00:49:19.870 --> 00:49:26.680
Even up in the northern Burma
with China, kids are giving me

00:49:26.680 --> 00:49:28.460
their Gmail accounts.

00:49:28.460 --> 00:49:31.060
So I think it's exciting and
there's opportunities.

00:49:31.060 --> 00:49:34.650
Even with our partners,
I can GTalk with them.

00:49:34.650 --> 00:49:37.360
Development's changed completely
since 30 years ago

00:49:37.360 --> 00:49:40.120
when I went out to a remote area
and you'd send a telex

00:49:40.120 --> 00:49:42.380
