things are going.

00:49:42.380 --> 00:49:45.140
It's exciting and there's
a lot of opportunity.

00:49:45.140 --> 00:49:49.010
At the same time, there's
also a lot of risk.

00:49:49.010 --> 00:49:51.720
A lot of opportunities that
these young people don't know

00:49:51.720 --> 00:49:56.220
how to evaluate or understand
or be savvy with.

00:49:56.220 --> 00:49:59.430
They don't have the worldview
to be able to move with this

00:49:59.430 --> 00:50:01.790
technology safely.

00:50:01.790 --> 00:50:02.610
So it's a mix.

00:50:02.610 --> 00:50:06.440
